# ========================================================================
# NOTES
# ========================================================================
# 
# 301 = Permanent redirect (search engines follow, updates crawl)
# 302 = Temporary redirect (for A/B testing, campaigns)
# 200 = Rewrite (URL stays in browser, invisible to user - good for SPA)
#
# UTM Parameters in shortcuts:
# - utm_source: 'orbit' identifies the source
# - utm_medium: 'shortlink' identifies marketing channel
# - utm_campaign: Optional, can be added per campaign
#
# These allow tracking of shortened link performance in GA4
# Example: /spotify link clicks → GA4 event with utm params
#
# ========================================================================
